    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wow that's a really powerful way to put it. you're saying basically that the whole meritocracy argument is just a way to protect the people at the top. do you think there's any actual legitimacy to the idea that wealth redistribution is \"fair\" to those who have worked hard to build their own wealth, or is that just another false narrative used to fight against equity?",
